\begin_layout Standard
The 
\family typewriter
GPlotFun
\family default
 package is a collection of gretl scripts and functions for advanced plotting
 methods.
 Gretl plotting facility makes heavy use of the well-known open-source graphing
 utility named Gnuplot (URL: 
\begin_inset CommandInset href
LatexCommand href
name "http://www.gnuplot.info/"
target "http://www.gnuplot.info/"
literal "false"

\end_inset

).
\end_layout

